dcterms:creator: Joe H. Chow
Juan J. Sanchez-Gasca
dcterms:description: Data for the IEEE 68 bus system is used, where the active power generation for each of the 16 generator buses is varied randomly between 70-150% of the base case. The load active and reactive powers at each of the 52 load buses are also varied randomly between 70-150% of the base case. This generates 6253 data points with 56% safe cases and 44% unsafe cases.
dcterms:title: IEEE 68 Bus System

dcterms:creator: J. H. Chow
dcterms:description: Data for the NPCC 140 bus system is used, where the active power generation, load active and reactive powers are varied randomly between 70-150%. This generates 4725 data points with 29% safe cases and 71% unsafe cases.
dcterms:title: NPCC 140 Bus System
